txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Jagged beaks from the birds near Trestlebridge. Deliver the items to Guardsman Otley in the town of Trestlebridge.
'We may not be able to recover their farms or homes but this may hearten some of the farmers. Thank you.'
'Sometimes vengeance wins out. That is the case with this request. Many of the farmers reported seeing the black, winged birds circling their homesteads before the attacks and want retribution.'
Rangers of Esteld√≠n Task: Jagged Beaks
Guardsman Otley, in Trestlebridge, is awaiting delivery of jagged beaks at the war-torn town of Trestlebridge.
Deliver the jagged beaks to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge
You have been tasked with collecting jagged beaks from the birds near Trestlebridge.\n\nYou can deliver the items to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge.
Wanted: Jagged beaks from the birds near Trestlebridge.
